      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>A small <rs type="objectType">stele</rs> (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.75</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.37</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.25</measure>) with only one prepared face, slightly
recessed; above this a rough circle is the only trace of
decoration.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the prepared face (prepared area <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.39</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.255</measure>); the surface is very worn.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Irregular cursive hand , <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.015-0.02</measure>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date exact="none" cert="low" notBefore="0201" notAfter="0400">Third-fourth century</date> (formulae, penalty).</p>
      </div>

      <div n="text" lang="grc" type="edition">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
        <ab>
		<lb n="1"/><w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w lemma="τόπος">τόπος</w> <w lemma="εἰμί">ἐστὶν</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w><lb n="2"/><w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w lemma="πλάτας">πλάτας</w> <persName full="yes" type="aphrodisian" key="vitus1"><name reg="Βίτος">Βίτου</name> <orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">μονη</unclear></orig><lb n="3"/><persName key="*roticus" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name><gap reason="lost" extent="6" unit="character" dim="left"/><unclear reason="damage">ρ</unclear>ωτικου</name> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w><lb n="4"/><persName key="praulius" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Πραύλιος"><unclear reason="damage">Πρα</unclear>υλίου</name></persName> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <persName key="asterius2" type="aphrodisian" full="yes"><name reg="Ἀστέριος">Ἀστ<unclear reason="damage">ε</unclear><lb n="5" type="worddiv"/><unclear reason="damage">ρ</unclear>ίου</name></persName></persName></persName> <rs key="cursor" type="profession"><w lemma="κούρσωρ">κούρσορος</w></rs> <w lemma="ὁ">τῶν</w><lb n="6"/><rs type="dignity" key="semnotatos"><w lemma="σεμνός">σεμνοτάτων</w></rs> <rs type="subject" key="tribes"><w lemma="φυλή">φυλῶν</w></rs>.<lb n="7"/><w lemma="εἰ">εἴ</w> <w lemma="τις">τις</w> <w lemma="δέ"><unclear reason="damage">δὲ</unclear></w> <w lemma="βούλομαι">βου<unclear reason="damage">λ</unclear>ηθείη</w> <unclear reason="damage">Ι</unclear><lb n="8"/><w lemma="χωρίς">χωρὶς</w> <w lemma="γνῶσις"><unclear reason="damage">γνώσ</unclear>εως</w> <w lemma="ἐμός">ἐ<lb n="9" type="worddiv"/>μῆς</w> <w lemma="ἐνθάπτω">ἐνθάψαι</w> <w lemma="τις">τινὰ</w><lb n="10"/><w lemma="δίδωμι">δώσει</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῷ</w> <rs type="dignity" key="sanctissimus"><w lemma="ἱερός">ἱερωτάτῳ</w></rs><lb n="11"/><w lemma="ταμεῖον">ταμεί<unclear reason="damage">ῳ</unclear></w> <w lemma="χρυσός">χρυσοῦ</w><lb n="12"/><w lemma="λίτρα">λίτραν</w> <w lemma="εἷς">μίαν</w>.</ab> 
      </div>

      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
        <p>l. 4,  <foreign lang="grc">Παυλίου</foreign> Roueché, <bibl><title level="m">ALA</title></bibl>; <foreign lang="grc">Π<unclear reason="damage">ρα</unclear>υλίου</foreign> cj <bibl><author>Feissel</author> (<date value="1991" notBefore="1991" notAfter="1991" exact="both">1991</date>)</bibl>.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>The place and the platform are (the property) of <seg cert="low">Bitos</seg>
<supplied reason="lost">son of</supplied> <gap reason="lost"/>rotikos son of
Praulios, also known as Asterios, <term lang="la">cursor</term>, of the most revered <term lang="la">phylae</term>; if anyone should wish, without my
knowledge, to bury anyone in <supplied reason="subaudible">here</supplied>, he will give to the most sacred
treasury one pound of gold.</ab>
      </div>

      <div type="commentary">
        <head>Commentary</head>
        <p>See discussion at <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.10">IX.10</xref>; for the penalty, and its implications
for the date, see <xref type="eAla-text" n="IX.5">IX.5</xref>.</p>
      </div>

